title: Wickets at Streets of Woodfield closing
text: Add a message (optional) Success - Article sent! close Saturday is the last day for Wickets Bar & Grill in the Streets of Woodfield shopping center in Schaumburg. Daily Herald file photo Daily Herald report Wickets Bar & Grill next to the AMC Loews Theatres at Streets of Woodfield in Schaumburg will close permanently at the end of the business day Saturday, Oct. 17. The business had been open for four years and will not be relocating, according to a representative. No new tenant for the space Wickets is vacating has been announced. Share this page
